Package: GaussQuant
Title: Tidy R Interface to QuantLib for Quantitative Finance
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Eiichi", "Horigome", email = "besuke.poripori@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides reusable R interfaces to the SWIG version of QuantLib
    for fixed income, derivatives, credit, pricing engines, cashflows,
    risk analytics, and quantitative-finance workflows. GaussQuant is
    the formal successor to QuantLibGauss and uses QuantLib directly
    without depending on QuantLibGauss.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    QuantLib,
    tibble,
    dplyr,
    purrr,
    lubridate
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
